headline: Eli Lilly (LLY) Partners With Senderra For Innovative Digital Patient Care Solution
summary: Eli Lilly (LLY) recently introduced EBGLYSS through Senderra Specialty Pharmacy, targeting patients with atopic dermatitis, while enhancing patient and provider experiences via SenderraCare+. Despite these positive moves, Eli Lilly's stock faced a 15% decline over the last quarter. This can be viewed against the backdrop of record high trends in major indexes like Nasdaq during the same period.
